92
00:04:28,690 --> 00:04:30,610
We are brothers.

93
00:04:32,610 --> 00:04:34,250
Brother.

94
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,440
Thanks. Thanks.

95
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:41,930
When I'm really short of money,

96
00:04:42,170 --> 00:04:43,400
I'll ask for your help.

