00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:00,570
You're right.

226
00:09:01,250 --> 00:09:03,040
When I saw patients
in the Village Hospital,

227
00:09:03,210 --> 00:09:04,130
I once had five patients

228
00:09:04,210 --> 00:09:05,800
with hepatic hydatid disease
on one morning,

229
