00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:37,280
It's difficult

243
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:39,370
to solve such a problem by outside aid.

244
00:09:40,210 --> 00:09:41,570
We must build a trustworthy

245
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:42,850
and highly skilled

246
