00:11:23,330 --> 00:11:24,160
Why are you even worse

278
00:11:24,370 --> 00:11:25,040
than we amateurs

279
00:11:25,130 --> 00:11:26,160
in physical strength?

280
00:11:26,610 --> 00:11:27,640
Duojie,

281
00:11:27,970 --> 00:11:28,760
that's a little

282
00:11:28,850 --> 00:11:30,250
ungrateful.

